      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for taking a look at my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and honestly, she still has that fresh showroom magic. I\u2019ve kept her tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, so the paint is deep, glossy, and practically glows. There\u2019s one tiny, microscopic stone chip near the wheel well that you\u2019d honestly need a map to find, but other than that, she\u2019s as perfect as they come. I'm only parting with her to make some room in the garage for a new project, and I\u2019d love for her to go to someone who appreciates a truly cared-for machine. Swing by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I'm so head-over-heels for this ride!",
